mg alt="Money Saved From Our Services" class=fl src=/assets/images/cash-stack.png> <p>These funds are held for only a brief period of time, after that time elapses the agency responsible for them may be permitted to seize them permanently through a process called "escheatment."</p> <p>We believe it's wrong for private citizens to lose their funds to faceless government agencies (a system rooted in feudal 16th century England). We are determined to prevent this from happening to any person, including you.</p> <div class=clear></div></footer> <hr class=svelte-eoez4b> <div class="svelte-eoez4b footer-nav"><nav class=svelte-13psowt><ul class=svelte-13psowt><li class=svelte-13psowt><a class=svelte-13psowt href=.>Home</a></li> <li class=svelte-13psowt><a class=svelte-13psowt href=our-company>Our Company</a></li> <li class=svelte-13psowt><a class=svelte-13psowt href=how-it-works>How It Works</a></li> <li class=svelte-13psowt><a class=svelte-13psowt href=questions aria-current=page>Questions</a></li> <li class=svelte-13psowt><a class=svelte-13psowt href=contact>Contact</a></ul></nav></div></main></div></div> <script>__SAPPER__={baseUrl:"",preloaded:[void 0,{}]};if('serviceWorker' in navigator)navigator.serviceWorker.register('/service-worker.js');var s=document.createElement("script");try{new Function("if(0)import('')")();s.src="/client/client.0efcfe49.js";s.type="module";s.crossOrigin="use-credentials";}catch(e){s.src="/client/shimport@1.0.1.js";s.setAttribute("data-main","/client/client.0efcfe49.js")}document.head.appendChild(s)</script> 